{"content": "I need to multiply 460\u2089 \u00d7 775\u2089.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n\n460\u2089 = 4\u00d79\u00b2 + 6\u00d79\u00b9 + 0\u00d79\u2070 = 4\u00d781 + 6\u00d79 + 0 = 324 + 54 + 0 = 378\u2081\u2080\n\n775\u2089 = 7\u00d79\u00b2 + 7\u00d79\u00b9 + 5\u00d79\u2070 = 7\u00d781 + 7\u00d79 + 5 = 567 + 63 + 5 = 635\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n\n378 \u00d7 635 = 240,030\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n\n240030 \u00f7 9 = 26670 r 0\n26670 \u00f7 9 = 2963 r 3\n2963 \u00f7 9 = 329 r 2\n329 \u00f7 9 = 36 r 5\n36 \u00f7 9 = 4 r 0\n4 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 4\n\nReading from bottom to top: **405230\u2089**\n\n405230", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 827, "completion_tokens": 321}